🚀 The Resurgence: Phase 1 (Foundation)
This repository documents Phase 1 of my self-building journey. My goal is to master modern technology in parallel with scaling my retail business, creating a synergy between software engineering and Business.

🎯 The Mission: Parallel Growth
I am building a foundation that allows me to manage a high-growth business while staying at the cutting edge of tech. This isn't just about learning; it's about expanding my capacity to execute "stupidly great" ideas through code.

Dual-Track Focus: Mastering Python logic while simultaneously driving shop growth through social media and creative content.

The Habit: Establishing a lifestyle where coding and business management feed into each other.

Implementation: Learning with the intent to build tools that eventually automate or boost my business ventures.

✅ Phase 1 Milestones (Completed)
Python Mastery: 100% completion of the "Zero to Hero" curriculum with documented logic.

Operational Consistency: Maintained a daily commit streak alongside daily shop promotions and Instagram Reels.

Workflow: Balanced shop accounts, inventory, and orders with deep-work coding sessions.

Certification: Successfully earned the course completion certificate (linked in repository).

